TextBody:
Dear Danylo,

We can have a session to increase the disk space today from 3:00 or 4:00 PM Ukraine time today.
All we need is that the customer  makes a snapshot and increases the disk space from the virtualization environment prior to our meeting and then during the meeting he provides us SSH access.

Looking forward for your reply.

Best regards,
